<graph edgedefault="undirected"><node id="&quot;DWIGHT D. EISENHOWER&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Dwight D. Eisenhower is the 34th President of the United States and the grandfather of David Eisenhower."&lt;SEP&gt;"Dwight D. Eisenhower was the 34th President of the United States from 1953 to 1961 and served as a five-star general during World War II, including roles such as Supreme Commander of the Allied Expeditionary Forces in Europe."</data>
