<node id="&quot;SUPREME COMMANDER OF THE ALLIED EXPEDITIONARY FORCES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ROLE"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Supreme Commander of the Allied Expeditionary Forces was the highest command position Eisenhower held during World War II, overseeing the invasion of North Africa and France."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-c0628455552ee0d2dbd17480c6d18b38</data>
