<node id="&quot;34TH BATTALION (AUSTRALIA)&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"34th Battalion was an infantry unit of the 1st Australian Imperial Force (AIF) that served in World War I and World War II, primarily in the Illawarra region of New South Wales."</data>
