<node id="&quot;34TH ARMOURED BRIGADE (UNITED KINGDOM)&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"The 34th Armoured Brigade was an armoured brigade of the British Army that served in the Second World War, formed in 1941 and later part of the 79th Armoured Division."</data>
