</node>
<node id="&quot;MIEMSS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"MIEMSS stands for Maryland Institute for Emergency Medical Services Systems, a statewide EMS system founded by Dr. Cowley in 1972."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-b2821d62cd4c5aad9fe951ada9103c47</data>
