  <data key="d1">"The Director is the new person who takes over the Institute and decides to develop partnerships with Japanese institutes."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Director refers to the person in charge of directing the animated television series 'South Park', likely Trey Parker or Matt Stone, given their roles as co-creators."</data>
