  <data key="d1">"Jesus vs. Frosty is a short created by Matt Stone and Trey Parker in 1995, featuring early appearances of characters like Eric Cartman."&lt;SEP&gt;"Jesus vs. Frosty is a short created by Trey Parker and Matt Stone in 1992, featuring Stan Marsh."</data>
