</node>
<node id="&quot;WEST NILE VIRUS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"West Nile virus is a disease that spread across the United States after the first reported cases in Queens, New York in 1999, primarily affecting horses but also appearing in other species."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-127ebc0fa04611a47e70bf0d115ab30a</data>
