  <data key="d0">"ORGANISM"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Birds are the primary hosts for the West Nile virus before it spreads to mosquitoes and then to mammals."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-127ebc0fa04611a47e70bf0d115ab30a</data>
