<node id="&quot;SYNCYTIUM&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Syncytium is a type of tissue formed by cells that are electrically coupled, allowing them to function as a single unit, which is characteristic of cardiac muscle."</data>
